            <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" id="par_id3155351" role="paragraph" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:StyleApply">Assigns a style to the current paragraph, selected paragraphs, or to a selected object.</ahelp></paragraph>
